snippet.title: Santa Clicker Tycoon (Christmas Indie Game)
snippet.description:
Santa Clicker Tycoon
Author : PseudoBytes

------------------------------------------------------------------
Indie Games (3D)
- https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLBXI4aXCmjuivZhgr6-_N62pqp0Ol-rz8
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
You are Santa and it is your job to make enough presents tomake everyone 
happy during Christmas. The virus hit Santahard, as he has lost his entire workforce. 
So you must startfrom scratch, and make sure everyone has a happy Christmas.
Luckily you will be able to hire new elves, and other things,
with your newly created presents.
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
- - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -
ダウンロード （Itch.io :）
https://pseudobytes.itch.io/santa-clicker-tycoon
- - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -
